{"tid":2193344,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企人係耶撚","createTime":"2020-09-07T18:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T06:16:59.000Z","uid":375062,"like":61,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"26f74ecd6d64bf355c0569e0f4fa90fa4a88ee65","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"同佢地生活真係慘過食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都有翻開教會 keep住每個星期日都俾屋企人逼住翻 試過偷偷地唔翻一次半次 佢哋都比好多說話我聽<br />\n<br />\n細細個翻嗰陣已經成日被逼背聖經 唱詩歌 <br />\n食飯/訓教之前又要祈禱感謝主 做乜撚都要感謝主<br />\n仲要逼住日撚日讀聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰陣已經覺得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n到大個啲中學拍拖 無意中俾佢地發現咗嗰陣個男朋友係非基督徒  結果比佢哋屌到仆街 話一定要揾翻基督徒先可以一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時喺屋企燥燥地 連想講句粗口都唔得 忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之就好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦因爲咁一直都好想盡快搬岀嚟住 <br />\n<br />\n利伸：岀生於基督家庭 全家都係勁虔誠嗰啲基督徒 但我唔係"},{"pid":"f1c7b0da9b35a30b7af695388d7bdb93760c06c2","tid":2193344,"uid":9392,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀上帝"},{"pid":"ff23ac7c93db274c535cc087fc667111532050b0","tid":2193344,"uid":128102,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"試下係屋企拜神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426536fa8944fbb3996dfe13e01be71582db99b9","tid":2193344,"uid":295477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ff23ac7c93db274c535cc087fc667111532050b0","tid":2193344,"uid":128102,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"試下係屋企拜神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定好精彩"},{"pid":"7653e2bccae95cb944396ab37e9a0dc9a3c748ea","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:05:50.000Z","msg":"好明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都因為咁想搬出嚟"},{"pid":"8d56101878ffdf923c7c160c50afdf9550d079a6","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:11:35.000Z","msg":"我想結婚就咁簽張紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但就係因為咁嘈交<br />\n話一定要行禮 要係神嘅見證之下先得<br />\n仲話我唔咁做 佢地唔會嚟參加<br />\n好撚無奈"},{"pid":"e6c8838f7340c325368a9b762549ec5b3ef4abe3","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7653e2bccae95cb944396ab37e9a0dc9a3c748ea","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:05:50.000Z","msg":"好明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都因為咁想搬出嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:19:00.000Z","msg":"我都好想搬但冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b6e3952298f3e5542f464f19c10f5cfe47c70b","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":23,"dislike":7,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:20:12.000Z","msg":"無論係咩宗教，屋企人只要係宗教撚就無運行，呢班偽君子成撚日叫人尊重信仰，但有機會的話又係呢班友唔理其他人既意願強推自己D垃圾觀念，仲要用為你好既理由做包裝情緒勒索<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">食撚屎啦垃圾宗教撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"86e8ab9a2afafc837f95118c5cbfe95b5de0159a","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e6c8838f7340c325368a9b762549ec5b3ef4abe3","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7653e2bccae95cb944396ab37e9a0dc9