咁你本人會唔會對其他宗教信仰有興趣？"},{"pid":"5bb535e4061973a1d6ea035f877f09cc3bf37c98","tid":2193344,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:57:13.000Z","msg":"好慘 信教父母同弱會父母真係一線之差<br />\n耶穌比幾層樓我我就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86409eec582c6ce77d6b519b11a5534388ee40ca","tid":2193344,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f74ecd6d64bf355c0569e0f4fa90fa4a88ee65","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"同佢地生活真係慘過食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都有翻開教會 keep住每個星期日都俾屋企人逼住翻 試過偷偷地唔翻一次半次 佢哋都比好多說話我聽<br />\n<br />\n細細個翻嗰陣已經成日被逼背聖經 唱詩歌 <br />\n食飯/訓教之前又要祈禱感謝主 做乜撚都要感謝主<br />\n仲要逼住日撚日讀聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰陣已經覺得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n到大個啲中學拍拖 無意中俾佢地發現咗嗰陣個男朋友係非基督徒  結果比佢哋屌到仆街 話一定要揾翻基督徒先可以一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時喺屋企燥燥地 連想講句粗口都唔得 忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之就好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦因爲咁一直都好想盡快搬岀嚟住 <br />\n<br />\n利伸：岀生於基督家庭 全家都係勁虔誠嗰啲基督徒 但我唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:07:11.000Z","msg":"見到第一句都覺得 屌 exact7ly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1f6baebade0a4c880d547254aa34c84d3b476d","tid":2193344,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3903f7132e27d28be4f6294a17789995b4ee3873","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86e8ab9a2afafc837f95118c5cbfe95b5de0159a","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e6c8838f7340c325368a9b762549ec5b3ef4abe3","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:19:00.000Z","msg":"我都好想搬但冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:26:53.000Z","msg":"我識一個伊斯蘭教家庭背景既女仔，仲慘，佢老母話要嫁佢去沙特，因為果度最接近真主阿拉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:09:41.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑左出聲"},{"pid":"512d8536e4faa7ceb66112de9f6fe94870674500","tid":2193344,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:12:50.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f000cd23e8517ac4bcdc8865e8cd82c0a1ff7793","tid":2193344,"uid":8949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e4b03dad2325ea82c2e31e76b6d45a678f96fd1b","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11dfb09206037072fb840577021a7489115fab56","tid":2193344,"uid":373132,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T19:07:36.000Z","msg":"樓主你嗰啲都叫做正常呀。我屋企人都係耶撚，不過係靈恩派，之前細個跟佢哋返教會，佢哋會無啦啦上身，大笑大喊，又喺度講嗰啲方言。好撚似邪教咁撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n我好記得我細個有一次腸胃炎，我老母唔俾我睇醫生，話要靠上帝嘅大能去醫治。嗰陣時我已經痛到面青口唇白，但係我阿媽堅持唔帶我去睇醫生。不停咁為我禱告，咁我細個唔識野，戇鳩鳩咁跟住禱告。最後我痛到暈咗我阿媽先至送我去急症室。嗰個醫生話我係痛到休克，仲話如果我唔睇醫生，可能會冇命。<br />\n<br />\n我細個都比佢哋迫返教會，但係我大個咗學識反抗，死都唔撚返。佢哋一逼我返教會，我就發脾氣掟爛晒屋企啲嘢。跟住就走去撕爛啲聖經，跟住到我上咗中學我阿爸我阿媽先至唔逼我返教會。<br />\n<br />\n利益申報：依家係無神論者"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T19:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:14:49.000Z","msg":"有哮喘係唔係上帝叫你吸少啖氣？"},{"pid":"c8f7c9946d3cb448c58d03969ea0e0a31ba37a49","tid":2193344,"uid":158496,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:47:50.000Z","msg":"你屋企人信嘅只係宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信耶穌本身唔係要你守規矩，每日做你屋企人講個堆只係形式嘅行為。係咁嘅情況下，係人都辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n信仰本身唔係咁可怕，係人有時斷章取義，或者誤解信仰，搞到啲事本末倒置。<br />\n<br />\n宗教=/=信仰<br />\n<br />\n樓主辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb291b69c3324883fae9a3a0f5b264420a565abf","tid":2193344,"uid":160953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38f564270f6569f1cd2870b2ad817e7e8ec22157","tid":2193344,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:47:01.000Z","msg":"試下搞gay／les<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:49:02.000Z","msg":"你想佢俾老竇老母打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2fe6648d8fec2ddaca00969363450b96c885a8","tid":2193344,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:49:23.000Z","msg":"真，有屋企人係神職人員"},{"pid":"d8435ef4df458eba0998de6f14ea468786c56889","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f1f6baebade0a4c880d547254aa34c84d3b476d","tid":2193344,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3903f7132e27d28be4f6294a17789995b4ee3873","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86e8ab9a2afafc837f95118c5cbfe95b5de0159a","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac