ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"有嘅事安慰佢<br />\n<br />\n你還有主呀~"},{"pid":"0ed3724111d036e32942f8a82305345748948a07","tid":2193344,"uid":233071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f74ecd6d64bf355c0569e0f4fa90fa4a88ee65","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"同佢地生活真係慘過食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都有翻開教會 keep住每個星期日都俾屋企人逼住翻 試過偷偷地唔翻一次半次 佢哋都比好多說話我聽<br />\n<br />\n細細個翻嗰陣已經成日被逼背聖經 唱詩歌 <br />\n食飯/訓教之前又要祈禱感謝主 做乜撚都要感謝主<br />\n仲要逼住日撚日讀聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰陣已經覺得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n到大個啲中學拍拖 無意中俾佢地發現咗嗰陣個男朋友係非基督徒  結果比佢哋屌到仆街 話一定要揾翻基督徒先可以一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時喺屋企燥燥地 連想講句粗口都唔得 忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之就好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦因爲咁一直都好想盡快搬岀嚟住 <br />\n<br />\n利伸：岀生於基督家庭 全家都係勁虔誠嗰啲基督徒 但我唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"過左18其實真係唔關佢哋事<br />\n做耶L18歲後都要受洗多次喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b347fc5456ca6124748898c363ddb76ce6c537ea","tid":2193344,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:09:32.000Z","msg":"會唔會因為叛逆心而變得好淫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6b4798b46bde219524ed5f1a67c004ef4fb4c7","tid":2193344,"uid":335693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:12:18.000Z","msg":"細個講咗句，頂你唔順，佢話係粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008936ae610b4c0d4690c982c3d0146a33476d8e","tid":2193344,"uid":335693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3903f7132e27d28be4f6294a17789995b4ee3873","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86e8ab9a2afafc837f95118c5cbfe95b5de0159a","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e6c8838f7340c325368a9b762549ec5b3ef4abe3","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:19:00.000Z","msg":"我都好想搬但冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:26:53.000Z","msg":"我識一個伊斯蘭教家庭背景既女仔，仲慘，佢老母話要嫁佢去沙特，因為果度最接近真主阿拉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:13:41.000Z","msg":"結果點？有冇嫁？"},{"pid":"847a06fed6c09870ff56298753a78da9fdcbedd6","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"008936ae610b4c0d4690c982c3d0146a33476d8e","tid":2193344,"uid":335693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3903f7132e27d28be4f6294a17789995b4ee3873","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86e8ab9a2afafc837f95118c5cbfe95b5de0159a","tid":2193344,"uid":238769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:26:53.000Z","msg":"我識一個伊斯蘭教家庭背景既女仔，仲慘，佢老母話要嫁佢去沙特，因為果度最接近真主阿拉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:13:41.000Z","msg":"結果點？有冇嫁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:15:38.000Z","msg":"未知，佢仲讀緊大學，但佢老母成日話要佢一畢業就嫁出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c929f99e0fc004a3b0345fecbb78886cd8c9ba6a","tid":2193344,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"好多基督徒父母根本當呢個係宗教而唔係信仰。如果父母比多d關心，體諒同了解，多d為仔女祈禱，我相信d仔女唔會咁抗拒。年青人唔鍾意權威管住自己係好自然既，到佢地大個就會明白，自己都係一個經常會犯錯，只識怪人唔識怪自己既一個人。尤其當佢遇到困境難面對，以前聽到既信仰內容就會提醒佢試吓去依靠神，而真正既信仰或許慢慢就建議起黎！"},{"pid":"c3708e2b3aa0bf0e0ef523a7b062888aef0b5a4b","tid":2193344,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"耶撚好多藍底rip"},{"pid":"e27589ba8f7e4ab4749ff7c8b9b1e3662eb9a2ed","tid":2193344,"uid":361141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11dfb09206037072fb840577021a7489115fab56","tid":2193344,"uid":373132,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T19:07:36.000Z","msg":"樓主你嗰啲都叫做正常呀。我屋企人都係耶撚，不過係靈恩派，之前細個跟佢哋返教會，佢哋會無啦啦上身，大笑大喊，又喺度講嗰啲方言。好撚似邪教咁撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n我好記得我細個有一次腸胃炎，我老母唔俾我睇醫生，話要靠上帝嘅大能去醫治。嗰陣時我已經痛到面青口唇白，但係我阿媽堅持唔帶我去睇醫生。不停咁為我禱告，咁我細個唔識野，戇鳩鳩咁跟住禱告。最後我痛到暈咗我阿媽先至送我去急症室。嗰個醫生話我係痛到休克，仲話如果我唔睇醫生，可能會冇命。<br />\n<br />\n我細個都比佢哋迫返教會，但係我大個咗學識反抗，死都唔撚返。佢哋一逼我返教會，我就發脾氣掟爛晒屋企啲嘢。跟住就走去撕爛啲聖經，跟住到我上咗中學我阿爸我阿媽先至唔逼我返教會。<br />\n<br />\n利益申報：依家係無神論者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:29:48.000Z","msg":"巴打猛料"},{"pid":"6e46d3df0c5fa97f7cbbd74a7d9c209e074ab716","tid":2193344,"uid":2864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:35:03.000Z","msg":"老豆係牧師<br />\n照口口係屋企爆粗<br />\n屌埋佢老母都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1420c8cd66bd539834ff35423cee2bad166218ed","tid":2193344,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:37:56.000Z","msg":"我去過自己棟樓樓上<br />\n<br />\n有d屋企門口都貼感謝主<br />\n<br />\n有d直頭貼埋聖餐幅畫"},{"pid":"370e37fb5e45a15700f6715499dc49703379fe90","tid":2193344,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"其實點會頂得順唱d唔啱音嘅詩歌"},{"pid":"21baa4a87b28bb9841761521e49dbec8f5224600","tid":2193344,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"耶撚就冇，佛撚就有個。"},{"pid":"b7866982d1cd6b71d4dedbe6a76fc431989b00e1","tid":2193344,"uid":356078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T03:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3283865696684378d19613b24db8677aa6150216","tid":2193344,"uid":193703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"屋企人係 有親戚都係<br />\n老一輩喪禮請咗個牧師淨係喺度傳教<br />\n話在座各位都唔知幾時死啦好快d信etc<br />\n悼念安慰環節都冇 去到火葬前一刻仲講緊<br />\n都好難唔令人唔憎呢個宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老母仲話 傳教比你 有永生既福音咪係安慰囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278644772b243ed4d5ba28cc847ea911c2ed4640","tid":2193344,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"屌真係好憎宗教撚成撚日阻礙世界進步收撚柒皮啦"},{"pid":"aa69f51534d32ed928c04f5dc84c1ca148151c83","tid":2193344,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11dfb09206037072fb840577021a7489115fab56","tid":2193344,"uid":373132,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T19:07:36.000Z","msg":"樓主你嗰啲都叫做正常呀。我屋企人都係耶撚，不過係靈恩派，之前細個跟佢哋返教會，佢哋會無啦啦上身，大笑大喊，又喺度講嗰啲方言。好撚似邪教咁撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n我好記得我細個有一次腸胃炎，我老母唔俾我睇醫生，話要靠上帝嘅大能去醫治。嗰陣時我已經痛到面青口唇