8722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f74ecd6d64bf355c0569e0f4fa90fa4a88ee65","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"同佢地生活真係慘過食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都有翻開教會 keep住每個星期日都俾屋企人逼住翻 試過偷偷地唔翻一次半次 佢哋都比好多說話我聽<br />\n<br />\n細細個翻嗰陣已經成日被逼背聖經 唱詩歌 <br />\n食飯/訓教之前又要祈禱感謝主 做乜撚都要感謝主<br />\n仲要逼住日撚日讀聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰陣已經覺得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n到大個啲中學拍拖 無意中俾佢地發現咗嗰陣個男朋友係非基督徒  結果比佢哋屌到仆街 話一定要揾翻基督徒先可以一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時喺屋企燥燥地 連想講句粗口都唔得 忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之就好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦因爲咁一直都好想盡快搬岀嚟住 <br />\n<br />\n利伸：岀生於基督家庭 全家都係勁虔誠嗰啲基督徒 但我唔係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:54:30.000Z","msg":"咁你本人會唔會對其他宗教信仰有興趣？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:36:43.000Z","msg":"冇呀 唔信任何宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cca79851f3fec5a48729f269f6f8944b5d7e95","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d9d57dfecb9ef4224e72c57ba002ebd4dce7c2e","tid":2193344,"uid":192465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:57:12.000Z","msg":"想問下你屋企耶撚對香港過去一年大是大非有乜睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見太多偽善偽大愛雙重標準耶撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"佢哋深黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d5bde9d54567a65aea779c8892e9a504d8a28a","tid":2193344,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d8629c4be785c7a1e492d909d219a8429b236a","tid":2193344,"uid":375062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38f564270f6569f1cd2870b2ad817e7e8ec22157","tid":2193344,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-